@startuml

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  教师组卷发布考试时序图 — Black & White Style
'  南方职业学院在线考试系统
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────

!theme plain
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "monospace"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #000000
skinparam ActorBorderColor #000000
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorFontColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

title <size:16><b>教师组卷发布考试时序图</b></size>\n<size:11>南方职业学院在线考试系统  |  题目管理 → 试卷管理 → 考试管理</size>

actor "教师\n(Teacher)" as Teacher
participant "ManualPaperForm.vue\n(组卷页面)" as PaperForm
participant "API 层\n(paper.ts / question.ts / exam.ts)" as API
participant "QuestionController\n(题目管理)" as QuestionController
participant "QuestionService\n(题目服务)" as QuestionService
participant "QuestionMapper\n(题目数据层)" as QuestionMapper
participant "PaperController\n(试卷管理)" as PaperController
participant "PaperService\n(试卷服务)" as PaperService
participant "PaperMapper\n(试卷数据层)" as PaperMapper
participant "ExamController\n(考试管理)" as ExamController
participant "ExamService\n(考试服务)" as ExamService
participant "ExamMapper\n(考试数据层)" as ExamMapper
database "MySQL\n(数据库)" as MySQL

' ═══ 阶段一: 题库管理 ═══
== 阶段一: 题库管理 ==

Teacher -> PaperForm : 1. 添加题目到题库
PaperForm -> API : 2. POST /api/questions
API -> QuestionController : 3. save(question)
QuestionController -> QuestionService : 4. save(question)
QuestionService -> QuestionMapper : 5. insert(question)
QuestionMapper -> MySQL : 6. INSERT INTO questions\n(content, type, answer, ...)
MySQL --> QuestionMapper : 返回结果
QuestionMapper --> QuestionService : 返回成功
QuestionService --> QuestionController : 返回 Boolean
QuestionController --> API : Result.success(true)
API --> PaperForm : 200 OK
PaperForm --> Teacher : 题目添加成功

' ═══ 阶段二: 组卷 ═══
== 阶段二: 组卷 (手动 / 自动) ==

alt 组卷方式: 手动组卷
    Teacher -> PaperForm : 7. 填写试卷信息，手动选择题目
    PaperForm -> API : 8. POST /api/papers
    API -> PaperController : 9. save(paper)
    PaperController -> PaperService : 10. save(paper)
    PaperService -> PaperMapper : 11. insert(paper)
    PaperMapper -> MySQL : 12. INSERT INTO papers\n(name, questions, total_score, ...)
    MySQL --> PaperMapper : 返回结果
    PaperMapper --> PaperService : 返回成功
    PaperService --> PaperController : 返回 Boolean
    PaperController --> API : Result.success(true)
    API --> PaperForm : 200 OK
    PaperForm --> Teacher : 试卷创建成功 (状态: DRAFT)

else 组卷方式: 自动组卷
    Teacher -> PaperForm : 7. 配置组卷规则\n(题型/数量/难度/分数)
    PaperForm -> API : 8. POST /api/papers/auto-generate
    API -> PaperController : 9. autoGenerate(request)
    PaperController -> PaperService : 10. autoGenerate(request, teacherId)
    PaperService -> QuestionService : 11. list(wrapper)\n按 type/teacherId/subject/difficulty 筛选
    QuestionService --> PaperService : 返回符合条件的题目列表
    PaperService -> PaperService : 12. Collections.shuffle()\nFisher-Yates 洗牌随机抽题
    PaperService -> PaperService : 13. 计算总分，构建 Paper 对象
    PaperService -> PaperMapper : 14. insert(paper)
    PaperMapper -> MySQL : 15. INSERT INTO papers
    MySQL --> PaperMapper : 返回结果
    PaperMapper --> PaperService : 返回成功
    PaperService --> PaperController : 返回 Paper 对象
    PaperController --> API : Result.success(paper)
    API --> PaperForm : 200 OK
    PaperForm --> Teacher : 自动组卷成功 (状态: DRAFT)
end

' ═══ 阶段三: 创建考试 ═══
== 阶段三: 创建考试 ==

Teacher -> PaperForm : 15. 填写考试信息\n(名称/课程/时间/时长)
PaperForm -> API : 16. POST /api/exams
API -> ExamController : 17. save(examRequest)
ExamController -> PaperService : 18. getById(paperId)\n获取试卷确认总分
PaperService --> ExamController : 返回 Paper (含 totalScore)
ExamController -> ExamService : 19. save(exam)\nstatus = DRAFT
ExamService -> ExamMapper : 20. insert(exam)
ExamMapper -> MySQL : 21. INSERT INTO exams\n(title, paper_id, course_id, ...)
MySQL --> ExamMapper : 返回结果
ExamMapper --> ExamService : 返回成功
ExamService --> ExamController : 返回 Boolean
ExamController --> API : Result.success(true)
API --> PaperForm : 200 OK
PaperForm --> Teacher : 考试创建成功 (状态: 草稿)

' ═══ 阶段四: 发布考试 ═══
== 阶段四: 发布考试 ==

Teacher -> PaperForm : 22. 点击发布考试
PaperForm -> API : 23. POST /api/exams/{id}/publish
API -> ExamController : 24. publishExam(id)
ExamController -> ExamService : 25. checkOwnership(id, userId, role)\n验证权限
ExamService --> ExamController : 权限验证通过
ExamController -> ExamService : 26. publishExam(id)
ExamService -> ExamService : 27. 校验:\n- status == DRAFT?\n- 时间有效?\n- startedAt < endedAt?
ExamService -> ExamMapper : 28. UPDATE exams\nSET status = 'PUBLISHED'
ExamMapper -> MySQL : 29. UPDATE exams SET status='PUBLISHED'\nWHERE id=?
MySQL --> ExamMapper : 返回结果
ExamMapper --> ExamService : 返回成功
ExamService --> ExamController : 发布成功
ExamController --> API : Result.success()
API --> PaperForm : 200 OK
PaperForm --> Teacher : 考试发布成功\n学生端可见

footer 南方职业学院 © 2026  |  权限: @RequireRole(ADMIN, TEACHER)  |  数据隔离: 教师只能操作自己的数据
@enduml
